<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>What is Vapi? | Vapi</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Vapi is the developer platform for building voice AI agents. We handle the complex infrastructure so you can focus on creating great voice experiences.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="nav-container">
      <div class="nav-brand">
        <h1>Vapi</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/" class="nav-link active">Home</a>
        <a href="/chat/non-streaming" class="nav-link">Non Streaming</a>
        <a href="/api-reference/calls/create" class="nav-link">Create</a>
        <a href="/api-reference/files/delete" class="nav-link">Delete</a>
        <a href="/api" class="nav-link">Api</a>
        <a href="/assistants/quickstart" class="nav-link">Quickstart</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="main">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="hero-title">What is Vapi?</h1>
        <p class="hero-description">Vapi is the developer platform for building voice AI agents. We handle the complex infrastructure so you can focus on creating great voice experiences.</p>
        <div class="hero-content">
          <p><strong>Voice agents</strong> allow you to:</p>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>Have natural conversations with users</li>
            <li>Handle complex customer queries</li>
            <li>Automate voice-based workflows</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
          <h2>How voice agents work</h2>
          <p>Every Vapi assistant combines three core technologies:</p>
          <div class="tech-grid">
            <div class="tech-item">
              <h3>Speech-to-Text</h3>
              <p>Converts user speech into text that your agent can understand</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item">
              <h3>Large Language Model</h3>
              <p>Processes the conversation and generates intelligent responses</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item">
              <h3>Text-to-Speech</h3>
              <p>Converts responses back to natural speech</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
          <h2>Two ways to build voice agents</h2>
          <p>Vapi offers two main primitives, designed for different use cases:</p>
          <div class="approach-grid">
            <div class="approach-card">
              <h3>Assistants</h3>
              <p><strong>Best for:</strong> Most use cases and fast iteration</p>
              <p>Assistants use a single system prompt plus tools and structured responses</p>
            </div>
            <div class="approach-card">
              <h3>Squads</h3>
              <p><strong>Best for:</strong> Complex workflows</p>
              <p>Multiple assistants working together for sophisticated interactions</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
          <h2>Key capabilities</h2>
          <ul class="capabilities-list">
            <li><strong>Real-time conversations:</strong> Sub-600ms response times with natural turn-taking</li>
            <li><strong>Phone integration:</strong> Make and receive calls on any phone number</li>
            <li><strong>Web integration:</strong> Embed voice calls directly in your applications</li>
            <li><strong>Multi-language support:</strong> Handle conversations in multiple languages</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
          <h2>Choose your path</h2>
          <div class="path-grid">
            <div class="path-card">
              <h3>Phone Calls</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Create a voice agent for inbound/outbound calls</li>
                <li>Build customer support or sales automation</li>
                <li>Get started with no coding required</li>
              </ul>
              <p><em>Build your first voice agent in 5 minutes</em></p>
            </div>
            <div class="path-card">
              <h3>Web Integration</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Embed voice chat in your website</li>
                <li>Create voice-enabled applications</li>
                <li>Full API control and customization</li>
              </ul>
              <p><em>Perfect for developers who want full control</em></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
          <h2>Developer tools</h2>
          <h3>Vapi CLI</h3>
          <p>The Vapi CLI brings the full power of the platform to your terminal:</p>
          <div class="cli-info">
            <h4>CLI Overview</h4>
            <p>Install in seconds with:</p>
            <pre class="code-block">npm install -g @vapi/cli</pre>
            <p>Everything from the dashboard, now in your terminal</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
          <h2>Popular use cases</h2>
          <div class="use-case">
            <h3>Customer Support</h3>
            <p>Built with Assistants</p>
            <p>Automate inbound support calls with agents that can access your knowledge base and escalate to humans when needed.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <style>
    :root {
      --brand: #2563eb;
      --brand-alt: #1d4ed8;
      --bg: #ffffff;
      --surface: #f8fafc;
      --text: #0f172a;
      --muted: #64748b;
      
      --font-heading: "Inter", sans-serif;
      --font-body: "Inter", sans-serif;
      
      --space-0: 0px;
      --space-1: 4px;
      --space-2: 8px;
      --space-3: 12px;
      --space-4: 16px;
      --space-5: 20px;
      --space-6: 24px;
      --space-7: 28px;
      --space-8: 32px;
      --space-10: 40px;
      --space-12: 48px;
      --space-16: 64px;
      --space-20: 80px;
      
      --radius-sm: 4px;
      --radius-md: 8px;
      --radius-lg: 12px;
      
      --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      --shadow-md: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      color: var(--text);
      background-color: var(--bg);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .navbar {
      background: var(--surface);
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      padding: var(--space-4) 0;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
    }

    .nav-container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 var(--space-6);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .nav-brand h1 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--brand);
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: var(--space-8);
    }

    .nav-link {
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-4);
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }

    .nav-link:hover {
      color: var(--text);
      background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1);
    }

    .nav-link.active {
      color: var(--brand);
      background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1);
    }

    .main {
      padding: var(--space-16) 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 var(--space-6);
    }

    .section {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
    }

    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-20);
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    }

    .hero-description {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto var(--space-8);
    }

    .hero-content {
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .feature-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding-left: var(--space-6);
    }

    .feature-list li {
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    }

    .feature-list li::before {
      content: '•';
      color: var(--brand);
      position: absolute;
      left: calc(-1 * var(--space-6));
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: var(--space-8);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }

    .card h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 1.875rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    }

    .card h3 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    }

    .tech-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--space-6);
      margin-top: var(--space-6);
    }

    .tech-item {
      padding: var(--space-6);
      background: var(--bg);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }

    .approach-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--space-6);
      margin-top: var(--space-6);
    }

    .approach-card {
      padding: var(--space-6);
      background: var(--bg);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }

    .capabilities-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .capabilities-list li {
      padding: var(--space-4) 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      position: relative;
      padding-left: var(--space-6);
    }

    .capabilities-list li:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .capabilities-list li::before {
      content: '✓';
      color: var(--brand);
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .path-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--space-6);
      margin-top: var(--space-6);
    }

    .path-card {
      padding: var(--space-6);
      background: var(--bg);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }

    .path-card ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: var(--space-4) 0;
    }

    .path-card li {
      padding: var(--space-2) 0;
      position: relative;
      padding-left: var(--space-6);
    }

    .path-card li::before {
      content: '•';
      color: var(--brand);
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .cli-info {
      margin-top: var(--space-6);
      padding: var(--space-6);
      background: var(--bg);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }

    .cli-info h4 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }

    .code-block {
      background: #1e293b;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      padding: var(--space-4);
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      margin: var(--space-4) 0;
      overflow-x: auto;
    }

    .use-case {
      padding: var(--space-6);
      background: var(--bg);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      margin-top: var(--space-6);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-links {
        display: none;
      }
      
      .hero-title {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
      
      .hero-description {
        font-size: 1.125rem;
      }
      
      .container {
        padding: 0 var(--space-4);
      }
      
      .tech-grid,
      .approach-grid,
      .path-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</body>
</html>